	return `<!doctype html><html lang="zh-CN"><head><meta charset="utf-8"><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1"><title>UGK Task Marketplace</title><style>${css()}</style></head><body><div class="shell">${nav("")}<section class="hero"><div><div class="kicker">Official task marketplace</div><h1>${tasks.length} TASKS READY TO RUN</h1><p class="lede">UGK 官方 task 市场。复制安装命令、下载备份 zip、查看详情页。登录后可点赞、收藏,下载会进入统计。</p><div class="nav-actions"><a class="btn btn-primary" href="#catalog">Explore tasks</a><a class="btn btn-secondary" href="/api/auth/github">Sign in with GitHub</a></div></div><aside class="command-box"><div class="kicker">Lazy install</div><code>$ ugk task install video-downloader</code><p class="lede">安装源来自 Cloudflare Pages 官方 manifest,支持 task 自带 scripts。</p></aside></section><section class="stats" id="stats"><div class="stat"><strong>${tasks.length}</strong><span>Official tasks</span></div><div class="stat"><strong>${downloads}</strong><span>Seed downloads</span></div><div class="stat"><strong>${likes}</strong><span>Seed likes</span></div><div class="stat"><strong>${scripts}</strong><span>Bundled scripts</span></div></section><section id="catalog"><div class="toolbar"><input class="search" data-search placeholder="Search tasks, tags, platforms"><a class="btn btn-primary" href="/api/auth/github">Sign in with GitHub</a></div><div class="catalog">${tasks.map(taskCard).join("")}</div></section></div><footer class="footer"><div class="shell"><div><strong>UGK Task Marketplace</strong><p>Official seed catalog. User upload and moderation use GitHub login + D1 backend.</p></div><div><p>Primary actions use Binance yellow. Live stats use Pages Functions.</p></div></div></footer><script>${script()}</script></body></html>`;
